R I P    N O T E S
Nothing. 

Your most primal fears grab you on this new journey into survival horror from the creators of Resident Evil series. Suspicious and terrifying... The world's most renowned scientist has disappeared and you've been recruited to investigate on a mysterious, remote island. Suddenly, out of the mist appears a predator, which has haunted mankind's imagination for centuries... Experience pure terror!
* Beautifully rendered graphics in a fully 3-D polygonal environment.
* Photo-realistic, chilling graphics add to the already heart-thumping storyline.
* Match wits against the most terrifying creatures that ever walked the earth.
* Control the fate of special tactics agent, Regina, as she searches for the missing Dr. Kirk.